## Decision Framework

### Use CSR When:
- ✅ App requires authentication
- ✅ SEO is not important
- ✅ Frequent real-time updates
- ✅ Internal tools/dashboards
- ✅ Budget/complexity constraints

### Use SSR When:
- ✅ SEO is critical
- ✅ Social sharing important
- ✅ Content is the product
- ✅ First impression matters
- ✅ Public-facing pages

### Use SSG (Static) When:
- ✅ Content rarely changes
- ✅ Can pre-render everything
- ✅ Maximum performance needed
- ✅ Predictable content structure

